This series includes records from the extinct First Baptist Church in Jaffrey, NH.
            Types of records include: meeting minutes for several church societies; annual reports;
            letters of dismission; membership lists; property deeds.

This series includes records from the extinct First Universalist Society in Jaffrey,
            NH. Types of records include: yearbooks; annual meeting reports; trustees reports;
            treasurer's and collector's reports; sales receipts; church histories.

This series includes records from The United Church in Jaffrey, NH. Types of records
            include: meeting minutes for several church societies; annual meeting minutes; deeds;
            building records; news clippings; newsletters; membership lists; constitution.
